            <p props="cpp">If the method call succeeds, returns the currently set mirror mode. See <xref keyref="RteVideoMirrorMode"/>.</p>
            <p props="android">If the method call succeeds, returns the video mirror mode. See <xref keyref="RteVideoMirrorMode"/>.</p>
